title: Dak’s Deal, What You People Don’t Realize, & Sarah Thomas
itunes:title: Dak’s Deal, What You People Don’t Realize, & Sarah Thomas
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including Dak Prescott's big contract (11:20), the Chiefs rebuilding their offensive line (25:20), and the Saints are making some more moves (34:50). The heroes spin through some more cuts in the league (46:11) and drop some knowledge in one of our favorite segments,  "What YOU people don't realize" (49:52). Ricky Hollywood sits down with the first female official in the NFL, Sarah Thomas (1:16:20)
